'''Rooj''' was a type of [[Plant/Legends|plant]] found on [[Jwlio]]. It may have been a type of [[Grass/Legends|grass]] and may have gone extinct due to the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] using defoliant and the mass quantities the [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] were eating.

